      <a href="/property-worth" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#b98229; color:#191817; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;border-radius:8px;">Request an Appraisal</a>
